       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">World of Warcraft Review</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Fricka</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">May 27, 2004, 11:42</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=World%20of%20Warcraft%20Review&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_29.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
